                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160403-142-off702 t18160403-142-cd703"></join>, three spoons, value 40s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18160403-142-victim1049" type="victimName">
                        Sarah 
                        Smith
                     <interp inst="t18160403-142-victim1049" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
